Snotel

AnnaClaire Marley

6/18/2020

This RMarkdown conducts initial time series analyses on two SNOTEL sites in the Chuska Mountains located in the Navajo Nation.

Read in packages

library(RNRCS)
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
library(gridExtra)
library(measurements)
library(mltools)
library(dataRetrieval)
